       83,
       "functools.partial.__doc__.__len__() == 83 — the docstring 'Create a new function with partial application of the given arguments\\nand keywords.' is exactly 83 characters; str.__len__() returns 83; verified with Python 3.14.3"]
    - [partial_doc_not_bytes,
